---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout
  lang="en"
  pathname="/privacy/"
  title="Privacy Policy — Nantian Gateway"
  description="Privacy Policy for the Nantian Gateway open-source project and documentation website."
  heading="Privacy Policy"
  intro="Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains what information we collect, and how it is managed."
>
  <section>
    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>
      Nantian Gateway is an open-source project. This Privacy Policy governs your use of our static documentation website, <strong>nantian.dev</strong>. We are committed to transparency and respect for our users' privacy.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
    <p>
      Because nantian.dev is a statically compiled website, we do not require user accounts, logins, or registration.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>We do not collect personal identifiers such as names, email addresses, or phone numbers.</li>
      <li>We do not collect financial or payment information.</li>
      <li>We do not track or compile browser habits or personal histories.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Hosting & Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      Our website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may process basic server logs (such as IP addresses and browser user-agent strings) to securely serve files, mitigate DDoS attacks, and provide anonymous, aggregate traffic statistics (e.g., number of visitors per day). This aggregate data does not identify individual users and is processed according to Cloudflare's privacy protocols.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>
      This website contains links to other external web services, primarily GitHub. We are not responsible for the privacy practices, content, or cookie management of these external sites. Please refer to their respective privacy policies for more information.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Updates to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may occasionally update this Privacy Policy. Any changes will be published directly on this page, with the effective date updated below.
    </p>
    <p class="muted">
      Last Updated: June 10, 2026
    </p>
  </section>
</ContentLayout>
